snippet.title: Fake Feminism Has To Stop (Hindi) Johnny Depp V/S Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Jhonny Depp V/S Amber Heard (Hindi). Fake Feminism Has To End. 

Feminism is about 'Equality' but do you really see any. Amidst Neha Dhupia's It's her choice and Bois locker room we've got this controversy going on right now. 

Modern day feminism will be the end of harmony. Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. What will happen   in the verdict. 

I made this video is Hindi because i wanted it to reach a wider Indian audience. This Epidemic is not just happening in our country. It's everywhere if you look around. This is what our 'Modern' day society has come to.

When a movie like Thappad is released it gets all the accolades from the critics but what about when the roles are reversed. No one bats an eye. Yehi duniya hai mere dost.
